description:
This app was designed to allow players of Call of Duty Black Ops to quickly and easily view the emblems of each level of prestige from Black Ops. The purpose of this app is to provide a recall of the emblems so that players know what prestige other players are in order to better assess that player's skill level by using a combination of their combat record stats and their level of prestige. This is useful because players may have prestiged over time as opposed to other players who earned their prestige quickly with a high skill level.

DISCLAIMER:Call of Duty is a registered trademark and Black Ops is a trademark of Activision Publishing Inc.

Also check out Black Ops Unlocked for the ultimate guide to multiplayer.

NOTE: First app by Path A Development. Made with the Palm Ares Development Tool.
